            <img src="../images/143301_2574435.jpg" alt="Red Rash" title="Sasayama Tadayasu
Japanese, born 1939, Red Rash"  />          </div>

    <p class="tools">
                    <a href="../artwork/191665/zoomify" class="zoomify-link"><strong>Zoom</strong> image</a><br />
